org.asterope.healpix
Class PixToolsVector3d

java.lang.Object
  org.asterope.healpix.PixToolsVector3d

public class PixToolsVector3d
extends java.lang.Object

A 3 element vector that is represented by double precision floating point x,y,z coordinates. If this value represents a normal, then it should be normalized. Mutable version was originally part of java3d vecmath package, was replaced with immutable version inside PixTools jar
